'''''The Rugrats Movie''''' is a traditional 2D platform [[video game]] based on the [[The Rugrats Movie|movie of the same name]] from the [[Nickelodeon (TV channel)|Nickelodeon]] animated series, ''[[Rugrats]]''.

== Gameplay ==
[[Tommy Pickles]]' little brother ([[Dil Pickles|Dil]]) has vanished without a trace and it is up to the Rugrats to find a replacement baby for Dil Pickles. The game features eight levels including Pickles house, the hospital, woods, and ancient ruins. There are two levels in which you drive the Reptar Wagon in a top-down perspective, but the rest features standard side-scrolling platform gameplay. In each level the player has to collect specific items and get to the exit before time runs out.

